    "chapter_position": "Chapter 17 (Śraddhātraya-Vibhāga-Yoga (The Yoga of Distinction of Threefold Faith)), verse 18",
    "speaker": "Krishna",
    "addressed_to": "Arjuna"
  },
  "word_by_word": [
